g.title: j3565942251
g.text: Do you know much of death?

g.title: j2243222524
g.text: And here I thought *I* was morbid... Are you okay?

g.title: j1090851610
g.text: LOL. Lady, don't get me started. You?

g.title: j1371165912
g.text: You seriously need to get outside more often.

g.title: j3978223251
g.text: La Flaca and I know each other well

g.title: j2921151725
g.text: Even if sometimes I don't want to like her
But she shepherds the ones I care for

g.title: j1651622024
g.text: But you're a medic. Don't you heal people? How can you "respect" death?

g.title: j1402843602
g.text: Death isn't a person. It's a thing that happens.

g.title: j2676230945
g.text: You're thinking about it all wrong

g.title: j4222305474
g.text: Do you blame her for ending your pain?
Was it her fault you suffered or was it the ones who hurt you to blame

g.title: j3632685347
g.text: My job is to make sure she takes people when it is their time
Not until she rips them from my hands
And not a damn second sooner

g.title: j1978772250
g.text: I make sure she knows she is welcome
She is not to be feared, but respected

g.title: j622431416
g.text: When I was in Duviri, and I knew I was about to die, sometimes it was a relief to know it'd be over soon.

g.title: j2894234339
g.text: I guess part of me understands that. Even if I don't like the idea of dying.

g.title: j4051959791
g.text: I am... going to stop this conversation, now.

g.title: j452581298
g.text: That no matter how badly it was about to hurt, the darkness would come and it'd be done.

g.title: j2187109909
g.text: To make sure La Flaca is certain in who she is taking
And that she ONLY gets who she needs

g.title: j1734494352
g.text: But I also knew I was going to come back.

g.title: j966576401
g.text: But I don't think it means everybody should die. lol

g.title: j288027950
g.text: We've all seen her sent loved ones too soon by the actions of others...

g.title: j1155382693
g.text: Maybe not as literally as you jaja
Though... now we are fantasmas, too

g.title: j4242302018
g.text: Caught in the same endless cycle as you were...

g.title: j2116560960
g.text: I need to go back to work
